comments.content:
Finally, something I can ID! I am not sure if this is the original work, but it's Dominator: [http://www.pixellogo.com/product.php?productid=16783&cat=333&page=1](http://web.archive.org/web/20071114011921/http:/www.pixellogo.com/product.php?productid=16783&cat=333&page=1)   
   
I looked but couldn't find it on any other sites with that same name, so I will assume that's the original font unless someone corrects me.

Great ID Brandee!! It's something I would have never guessed, and I guess it's not so familiar. Thanks a million.   
   
Does anyone know who own's the design to Dominator? I recognize some of those from the [Brainreactor](http://web.archive.org/web/20071114011921/http:/www.abstructure.com/old_index.html) fontpack but Dominator is not there. Any ideas?
I knew this font style looked familiar. Bought the [Brain Reactor Fonts pack](http://web.archive.org/web/20071114011921/http:/www.mindcandy.com/fonts/brainreactor/index.html) years ago...
